OL,4,Cspirals beyond other developed
OL,5,Ceconomies
OL,7,FThroughout 2024, the IMF has
OL,8,Frepeatedly highlighted the need for
OL,9,Faction in the UK, as ITV News Business
OL,10,Fand Economics Editor Joel Hills
OL,11,Freports from Washington
OL,13,FThe International Monetary Fund (IMF)
OL,14,Fhas repeated its warning that the
OL,15,Ffinances of the UK government cannot
OL,16,Fbe sustained without either cuts to
OL,17,Fthe scope of the welfare state or
OL,18,Fincreases in taxes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
