OL,3,CUK urged to rein in spending as debt
OL,4,Cspirals beyond other developed
OL,5,Ceconomies
OL,7,F"In many countries, primary balances,
OL,8,Fthe difference between fiscal revenues
OL,9,Fand pubic expenditure net of debt
OL,10,Fservice, needs to improve," Gourinchas
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FThe IMF names the UK, US, France,
OL,14,FItaly, South Africa and Brazil as
OL,15,Fcountries that need to take immediate
OL,16,Fsteps to prevent national debt from
OL,17,Fincreasing further.
