OL,3,CUK urged to rein in spending as debt
OL,4,Cspirals beyond other developed
OL,5,Ceconomies
OL,7,FThat's a bigger increase than in the
OL,8,FUnited States (49), Greece and Spain
OL,9,F(both 56), plus Portugal (37) -
OL,10,Fcountries we perhaps like to think of
OL,11,Fas being in a worse economic shape
OL,12,Fthan the UK.
OL,14,FOf the advanced economies, only
OL,15,FJapan's debt-to-GDP ratio has risen by
OL,16,Fmore (63) than the UK's.
OL,18,FHas the UK government taken heed of
OL,19,Fthe IMF's warnings?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
