OL,7,FChancellor Rachel Reeves will travel
OL,8,Fto Washington later this week ahead of
OL,9,Fher Budget on October 30.
OL,11,FReeves is a recent convert to the
OL,12,FIMF's view of the UK's public finances.
OL,14,FShe spent the election campaign in
OL,15,FJune insisting the only taxes that
OL,16,Fwould rise under a Labour government
OL,17,Fwere those set out in the party's
OL,18,Fmanifesto.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
