OL,7,FAfter becoming Chancellor, she
OL,8,Fannounced that she had discovered
OL,9,Fthings were in a much worse state than
OL,10,Fshe had previously thought, and that
OL,11,Fadditional tax rises and spending cuts
OL,12,Fwould be necessary.
OL,14,FWhat is interesting is that throughout
OL,15,F2024, the IMF has repeatedly
OL,16,Fhighlighted the need for action in the
OL,17,FUK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
