OL,7,FIn January, it explicitly called on
OL,8,Fthen-chancellor Jeremy Hunt not to cut
OL,9,Ftaxes further in his March budget. He
OL,10,Fignored the advice.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FIn April, the IMF named the UK as one
OL,18,Fof four countries which urgently
OL,19,Fneeded to take steps "to address
OL,20,Ffundamental imbalances between
OL,21,Fspending and revenues".
