OL,3,CUK urged to rein in spending as debt
OL,4,Cspirals beyond other developed
OL,5,Ceconomies
OL,7,FThe IMF even recommended ways in which
OL,8,Fthe hole could be filled, including
OL,9,Fscrapping the triple-Lock on pensions,
OL,10,Fbroadening the bases for VAT and
OL,11,Finheritance tax, also reforming
OL,12,Fcapital gains and property taxation.
OL,14,FIn the end, the IMF's call for fiscal
OL,15,Fconsolidation (of around 1% of GDP)
OL,16,Fand its advice on how best to deliver
OL,17,Fit was ignored by Labour and every
OL,18,Fother political party.
